    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方交流群：727842837</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >带上你的房子去旅行吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款你扮演的主角开着建造在火车上的房子去旅行的游戏。你可以采集资源，升级、改造你的火车和房屋，克服各种障碍，探索曾经辉煌的火车国度毁灭后的世界，寻找先民的下落，找到历史的真相。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e30809f8d70003231476833a7a96bf2a.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e30809f8d70003231476833a7a96bf2a.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e30809f8d70003231476833a7a96bf2a.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶和升级各式各样的蒸汽机车，各种车型基于真实世界车型设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e1c9addb9d8cdeddc03246d318f6f2ff.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e1c9addb9d8cdeddc03246d318f6f2ff.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/e1c9addb9d8cdeddc03246d318f6f2ff.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以升级房屋尺寸，修改房屋建筑风格，增添内部家具，打造属于自己风格的火车屋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/b0e08a0b0f98d183602e5a54f8671a3b.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/b0e08a0b0f98d183602e5a54f8671a3b.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/b0e08a0b0f98d183602e5a54f8671a3b.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以进行采矿、伐木、耕种、烹饪、纺织、制作、研究等各种活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/985ec614aad9000341979cfae139f3d0.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/985ec614aad9000341979cfae139f3d0.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/985ec614aad9000341979cfae139f3d0.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过增加挂车来实现更多功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/00b00278f01bd3ff7cec2044b09f7e81.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/00b00278f01bd3ff7cec2044b09f7e81.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/00b00278f01bd3ff7cec2044b09f7e81.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非线性的铁路系统，在区域内自由探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/87424d2611afa8a350aff08fde915eb1.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/87424d2611afa8a350aff08fde915eb1.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/87424d2611afa8a350aff08fde915eb1.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探寻定居点，和居民进行交易，完成任务，探索宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/fea045e171344844855cd3eb809251d8.poster.avif?t=1731640169\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/fea045e171344844855cd3eb809251d8.webm?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326700/extras/fea045e171344844855cd3eb809251d8.mp4?t=1731640169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的风景和精心设计的摄像机视角，带来电影式的观看体验。</p>",
